{"incident_id": "5574", "summary_detail": {"base": "", "type": "text/html", "value": "D04-150-S-17FLATHEAD NATIONAL FOREST 650 Wolfpack Way Kalispell, MT 59901 Forest Supervisor\u2019s Order   TRAIL RESTRICTION ORDER   East Fork Strawberry Creek Trail #371, is closed due to fire behavior.   Pursuant to Title 36 Code of Federal Regulation 261.50 (b), the following restriction is in effect on the Spotted Bear Ranger District on the Flathead National Forest, Flathead County, Montana. This temporary restriction is in addition to those enumerated in Subpart A, Part 261, Title 36, Code of Federal Regulations. These restrictions become effective when signed and will remain in effect until rescinded. See the attached map, Exhibit A.    36 CFR 261.55 \u2013 Forest Development Trails:   Being on the trail [Title 36 CFR 261.55(a)]   The below listed National Forest System Trail located on the Spotted Bear Ranger District is closed to all public travel because of wildfire activity associated with the Strawberry Fire.   Description of Restricted National Forest Access     Trail #371, in...", "language": null}, "links": [{"href": "https://inciweb.nwcg.gov/incident/article/5574/39799/", "type": "text/html", "rel": "alternate"}], "published_parsed": null, "title": "8-29-17 Trail Closure due to Strawberry Fire, Order #D04-150-S-17 (Strawberry Fire Wildfire)", "summary": "D04-150-S-17FLATHEAD NATIONAL FOREST 650 Wolfpack Way Kalispell, MT 59901 Forest Supervisor\u2019s Order   TRAIL RESTRICTION ORDER   East Fork Strawberry Creek Trail #371, is closed due to fire behavior.   Pursuant to Title 36 Code of Federal Regulation 261.50 (b), the following restriction is in effect on the Spotted Bear Ranger District on the Flathead National Forest, Flathead County, Montana. This temporary restriction is in addition to those enumerated in Subpart A, Part 261, Title 36, Code of Federal Regulations. These restrictions become effective when signed and will remain in effect until rescinded. See the attached map, Exhibit A.    36 CFR 261.55 \u2013 Forest Development Trails:   Being on the trail [Title 36 CFR 261.55(a)]   The below listed National Forest System Trail located on the Spotted Bear Ranger District is closed to all public travel because of wildfire activity associated with the Strawberry Fire.   Description of Restricted National Forest Access     Trail #371, in...", "content": "<div id=\"content\">\n<h3>8-29-17 Trail Closure due to Strawberry Fire, Order #D04-150-S-17</h3><p><strong>Incident:</strong> Strawberry Fire Wildfire<br/><strong>Released:</strong> 9 min. ago</p>\n<!-- \ncached related article links at 18:30:14\ncached id c1ed3bf3a0461e99ca680e4039ba1cf8\n-->\n<div id=\"related_block\"><h4 id=\"related_head\">Related Information</h4><ul class=\"related_list\"><li><a href=\"https://inciweb.nwcg.gov/photos/MTFNF/2017-08-31-1811-Strawberry-Fire/related_files/pict20170802-182813-0.pdf\" rel=\"new\">Closure Map, Exhibit A, D04-150-S-17 (pdf 355 kb)</a></li></ul></div><p align=\"right\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><b><font face=\"'Times New Roman'\" size=\"4\">D04-150-S-17</font></b><br/></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\"><font face=\"Times\">FLATHEAD NATIONAL FOREST</font></font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">650 Wolfpack Way</font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\"><font face=\"Times\">Kalispell, MT 59901</font></font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">Forest Supervisor\u2019s Order</font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"><br/>TRAIL RESTRICTION ORDER</font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">East Fork Strawberry Creek Trail #371, is closed due to fire behavior.</font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><font face=\"Times\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\">Pursuant to Title 36 Code of Federal Regulation 261.50 (b), the following restriction is in effect on the Spotted Bear Ranger District on the Flathead National Forest, Flathead County, Montana. This temporary restriction is in addition to those enumerated in Subpart A, Part 261, Title 36, Code of Federal Regulations. These restrictions become effective when signed and will remain in effect until rescinded. </font></font><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"3\">See the attached map, Exhibit A. </font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">36 CFR 261.55 \u2013 Forest Development Trails:</font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">Being on the trail [Title 36 CFR 261.55(a)]</font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\"><font face=\"Times\">The below listed National Forest System Trail located on the Spotted Bear Ranger District is <b>closed to all public travel because of wildfire activity associated with the Strawberry Fire.</b></font></font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><b><u><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">Description of Restricted National Forest Access</font></u></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\"><font face=\"Times\"><b>Trail #371, </b>in its entirety, from the junction with Gateway Gorge Trail #322 (NW \u00bc of Section 35, R 11W, T 27N) to Strawberry Creek Trail #161 (NW \u00bc of Section 28, R 11W, T 27N).</font></font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\"> </font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">Exemptions:</font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\"> </font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">Pursuant to Title 36 CFR 261.50(e), the following are exempt from this restriction:</font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; text-indent: -22.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><font face=\"Times\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\">1. </font></font><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"3\">Persons with a permit issued by a forest officer specifically authorizing the otherwise prohibited act or omission.</font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; text-indent: -22.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><font face=\"Times\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\">2. </font></font><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"3\">Any Federal, State, or local officer, or member of an organized rescue or fire fighting force in the performance of an official duty.</font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">Done at Kalispell, Montana this _____day of September, 2017.</font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><font face=\"Times\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\">By: </font></font><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"3\">____________________________</font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">CHIP WEBER</font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\">Forest Supervisor</font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\"> </font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\"><font face=\"Times\"><b>Penalty: </b>Violation of these prohibitions is punishable by a fine of not more than $5,000 for an individual or $10,000 for an organization, or imprisonment for not more than 6 months, or both (16 USC 551 and 18 USC 3559 and 3571).</font></font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><b><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times\" size=\"3\"> </font></b></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\"><font face=\"Times\"><b>Notification: </b>A copy of this order shall be posted as prescribed in 36 CFR 261.51.</font></font></font></p><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"> </font>\n</div>", "guidislink": false, "title_detail": {"base": "", "type": "text/plain", "value": "8-29-17 Trail Closure due to Strawberry Fire, Order #D04-150-S-17 (Strawberry Fire Wildfire)", "language": null}, "link": "https://inciweb.nwcg.gov/incident/article/5574/39799/", "published": "Sat, 02 Sep 2017 18:21:00 -05:00", "article_id": "39799", "id": "https://inciweb.nwcg.gov/incident/article/5574/39799/"}